cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the analysis of network traffic and behavior of IoT devices in a home setting, with a focus on privacy and security risks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also discusses the impact of device behavior on bandwidth, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.SE (Software Engineering).
